Package: bizicount
Title: Bivariate Zero-Inflated Count Models Using Copulas
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A package for maximum likelihood estimation of copula-based zero-inflated (in addition to not zero-inflated) Poisson and negative binomial count models. Supports Frank and Gaussian copulas. Allows for mixed margins (e.g., one margin Poisson, the other ZINB), and several marginal link functions. Built-in methods for publication-quality tables using 'texreg', and post-estimation diagnostics using 'DHARMa'. 
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/jmniehaus/bizicount
bugreports: https://github.com/jmniehaus/bizicount
